Determine the values of `c` and `d` after the following code runs.

```java
int a = 17;
int b = 5;
int c = a / b;
int d = a % b;
```

What is the output of the following code?

```java
int x = 3;
int y = 4;
System.out.println("Sum: " + x + y);
System.out.println(x + y + " is the sum");
```

Determine the values of `y` and `z` after the following code runs.

```java
double x = 9.9;
int y = (int) x;
double z = (double) 7 / 2;
```

What is the output of the following code?

```java
String s = "Hello";
s = s + " World";
System.out.println(s);
String t = "Java";
t.substring(0, 2);
System.out.println(t);
```

Determine the values of `a`, `b`, and `c` after the following code runs.

```java
int n = 2345;
int a = n % 10;
int b = n / 10 % 10;
int c = n / 100 % 10;
```

